gnm:Cells.gnm:Cell: Transformation of geodetic (B,L,H - latitude, longitude, height) to geocentric (X,Y,Z) coordinates and back.
Ellipsoid sheet - contains the ellipsoid and zone parameters.
BLhtoXYZ sheet - calculating geodetic (B,L,h) to geocentric (X,Y,Z) coordinates
XYZtoBLh sheet - calculating geocentric (X,Y,Z) to geodetic (B,L,h) coordinates
